description: Welcome to Unit 8S at 154 W 8th Street! This bright and thoughtfully designed home features a chef’s kitchen with state-of-the-art Thermador appliances, sleek quartz countertops, and a layout that seamlessly connects to both a sun-filled corner living room and a dedicated dining area—perfect for entertaining or enjoying everyday meals. The spacious second bedroom, equipped with a high-end custom Murphy bed, effortlessly transforms into a versatile home office or comfortable guest space. The primary suite offers a serene retreat with a spa-like en-suite bathroom, providing a luxurious space to unwind. This exceptionally well-maintained building also boasts two heated garage parking spots, and a shared outdoor area with grills and lounge seating, creating an ideal spot for relaxation or hosting friends. Don’t miss the opportunity to experience everything this beautiful unit has to offer!
